1:39:46.748 --> 1:39:48.116
[ding]

1:40:30.692 --> 1:40:33.161
See you soon, Aubrey.

1:41:14.436 --> 1:41:16.504
Oh, yeah.

1:41:16.504 --> 1:41:17.672
Thanks.

1:41:32.754 --> 1:41:34.222
Thanks.

1:42:29.244 --> 1:42:31.312
Would you mind
if I had a moment alone

1:42:31.312 --> 1:42:32.780
